{#
  Shared compact topstrip — Wave 2.4 of the UI redesign (2026-06-03).

  Extracted from base.html.j2 so the dossier (which intentionally does
  NOT extend base) can include the same nav row instead of hand-
  maintaining its own copy. Before this partial existed the dossier's
  inline topstrip had diverged from base — missing the Intake link.

  Same chrome as before: <div class="topstrip"> with seven links on
  the left and a small view-toggle span on the right. The active link
  is styled via `class="is-active"` (rule in aegis-system.css); inactive
  links render unchanged.

  Inputs (all optional):
    active — one of "Today" | "Deals" | "Merchants" | "Funders"
             | "Upload" | "Intake" | "Review" | "CloseQueue"
             | "Portfolio" | "DisclosureEvents" | "Triage"
             | "BankLayouts" | "Admin";
             the matching link gets `class="is-active"`. Pages that do
             not highlight any nav (e.g. the dossier) simply omit
             `active`. ``Triage`` covers both /ui/triage and
             /ui/shadow-signals (the shadow signals page is reached via
             the Triage tile's drill-down). ``Admin`` covers both
             /ui/admin/applied-migrations and /ui/admin/audit-log (the
             audit-log page is reached from the migrations page header).
             U35 (2026-06-10): the Admin link now lands on
             /ui/admin/health (the "is everything OK?" status page);
             migrations + audit-log are reachable via the health page's
             header actions row.
    now    — display string for the right-hand view-toggle span. Same
             default convention as base.html.j2 (falls back to '').
#}
<div class="topstrip">
  <div class="links">
    {% set _active = active|default('') %}
    <a href="/ui/"          {% if _active == 'Today'     %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Today</a>
    <a href="/ui/deals"     {% if _active == 'Deals'     %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Deals</a>
    <a href="/ui/merchants" {% if _active == 'Merchants' %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Merchants</a>
    <a href="/ui/funders"   {% if _active == 'Funders'   %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Funders</a>
    <a href="/ui/upload"    {% if _active == 'Upload'    %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Upload</a>
    <a href="/ui/intake"    {% if _active == 'Intake'    %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Intake</a>
    <a href="/ui/review"    {% if _active == 'Review'    %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Review queue</a>
    <a href="/ui/close-queue" {% if _active == 'CloseQueue' %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Close queue</a>
    <a href="/ui/portfolio" {% if _active == 'Portfolio' %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Portfolio</a>
    <a href="/ui/disclosure-events" {% if _active == 'DisclosureEvents' %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Disclosure events</a>
    <a href="/ui/triage" {% if _active == 'Triage' %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Triage</a>
    <a href="/ui/bank-layouts" {% if _active == 'BankLayouts' %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Bank layouts</a>
    <a href="/ui/admin/health" {% if _active == 'Admin' %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>Admin</a>
  </div>
  <div class="view-toggle">
    <span style="color:var(--sage)">aegis · {{ now|default('') }}</span>
  </div>
</div>
